{"type": "article", "id": 20304, "title": "巧克力包装", "description": "", "date": "2016-01-06T07:00:22Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 42, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606151813GAxDTRlYHQ7m43IJ.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这组巧克力包装做成了一本小书，是长方形的盒子，可以像书页一样打开，有神圣感。它的 logo 带有明显的宗教含义，五种巧克力的封面一起组成“SAINT”的文字，但用了近似于手绘的表现方式，在复古的元素中显得很可爱。对应着圣诞节、复活节另有特别版。设计师来自土耳其，这个项目想让儿童忽略不同种族、语言和宗教，获得最纯真的快乐。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606151810vlcuD5awAdUf0h7r.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606061518118Q5Gj2IuMcxNmpKB.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606151811CFgKoxQHbnwztI9G.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.02592593\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606061518120r86mPnbp5czZBeA.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606151812kbGR3wI2jmczu9EO.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.29537037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}